name: Multifaceted Tokyo
description: Multifaceted Tokyo consists of a series of photographs taken during a one-day walking tour of Tokyo, and curated from the most memorable and decisive moments. Tokyo is a city full of multifaceted charm, blending modern with historical. The unique combinations of human motion, geometric patterns, modern architecture and the sophisticated atmosphere of the city became my muse. I hope that this collection enables the viewer to feel the quirky charm of Tokyo, while evoking a sense of curiosity.
